{"title":"法官的公文包","authors":["黄东成"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":7,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"法官的公文包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄东成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经久了雨淋日晒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑皮上，几缕淡淡的渍印。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛黑发里出现几丝白发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记录下走过的荒径。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滥用的权力还能挤压它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——藏匿起罪行的明证？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的呼声定能唤醒它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——抖露出事实，抖露真情！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今，它闪现着法制的尊严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"承负着党中央的决心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔波在里弄，是群众的知音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屹立在法庭，是罪犯的枷锁！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}